+---
+description: Three knowledge silos — block cross-RAG between Kunskap, Valv-Chat, and Barnen
+alwaysApply: false
+globs: functions/src/lib/*Rag*.ts,functions/src/agents/*Vault*.ts,functions/src/agents/valv*.ts,functions/src/agents/knowledge*.ts
+---
+
+# Memory Silo Guard
+
+Tre kunskapsytor — **MUST NOT** cross-RAG. Kanon: `.context/arkiv-minne.md`.
+
+## Silos
+
+| Silo | Collections | Callable |
+|------|-------------|----------|
+| Kunskap | `kampspar`, `kb_docs` | `knowledgeVaultQuery` |
+| Valv | `reality_vault` | `valvChatQuery` |
+| Barnen | `children_logs` | Dossier read; future dedicated callable (G8) |
+
+## Red flags (block merge)
+
+- `knowledgeVaultQuery` / `kampsparQueryRag` reading `reality_vault` or `children_logs`
+- `valvChatQuery` / `vaultRag` reading `kampspar` or `kb_docs`
+- Single "search everything" UI without silo labels
+- Shared vector namespace mixing bevis + livsminne without isolation
+
+## Allowed cross-reads (not user-facing RAG)
+
+- **Vävaren** (`kampsparRag.ts`): journal + valv metadata for tagging only
+- **Dossier**: explicit user-selected sources in wizard
+- **Speglar**: client token-match on valv — Zero Footprint, not stored RAG
+
+## Agent mapping (vision S20)
+
+- **Livs-Arkivarien** → Kunskap-RAG only (`agent_livs_arkivarien`)
+- **Sannings-Analytikern** → Valv (`valvChatQuery`, Dossier) — not Livs-Arkivarien
+
+## References
+
+- Skill: `.cursor/skills/livskompassen-memory-silo-guard/SKILL.md`
+- Vision: `docs/specs/incoming/Vision-AI-Native-Blueprint.md` § S01–S02, S20
