+---
+description: ADK SynapseBus, auto-ingest triggers, and Zero Footprint synapse state
+alwaysApply: false
+globs: functions/src/adk/**,functions/src/adk/synapses/**
+---
+
+# Synapser & ADK
+
+Sub-synaptiskt nätverk — **inte** samma som Firestore `SystemSynapse` blueprint (G9).
+
+## Triggers (`synapseBus.ts`)
+
+| Trigger | Status | Mål |
+|---------|--------|-----|
+| `drive_file_ingested` | **live** | `kb_docs` via `driveIngestSynapse.ts` |
+| `user_overwhelm` | **live** | Paralys-Brytaren mikrosteg |
+| `journal_woven` | **stub** | Log only — G7 |
+| `dcap_alert` | **stub** | Log only |
+
+## MUST
+
+- Hash payloads in synapse state — no raw PII (`hashPayload` in `stateStore.ts`).
+- Clear synapse state on logout (`clearSynapseState`).
+- Drive ingest → **`kb_docs` only** — never auto-write `reality_vault`.
+- Route through `AdkOrchestrator.emitSynapse` — do not bypass with ad-hoc Firestore writes.
+
+## MUST NOT
+
+- Persist user content in synapse RAM across sessions (Zero Footprint).
+- Mix ADK synapse triggers with CSS/UI "synaps" naming as data layer.
+- Auto-ingest journal or trauma content to `kampspar` without explicit opt-in.
+
+## References
+
+- Skill: `.cursor/skills/livskompassen-synapser-adk/SKILL.md`
+- Vision: `docs/specs/incoming/Vision-AI-Native-Blueprint.md` § S04, S20
